.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "22 AOUT 2024"

.SH NAME
hsh \- program which emulates a shell terminal with its options.

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <sys/types.h>
.B #include <sys/wait.h>
.B include <stdlib.h>
.B include <unistd.h>
.B include <stdio.h>
.B include <string.h>

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hsh
This program is used to emulate a shell environment.

.TP
.B ls
Lists all files

.B cd 
Changes directories

.B pwd
Shows the current path

.B whoami
Shows the current user's ID

.SH RETURN VALUE
The program
.B hsh
returns the result of the child process asked by the current user.

.SH ERRORS
In case of the
.B hsh
program malfunctioning, it will return an error message.

.SH EXAMPLE
$ ./hsh

ls 

